msgid "Read and write emails"
msgstr "E-postak irakurri eta idatzi"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.mail.metainfo.xml:18
msgid ""
"Merkuro Mail is a free and open source email client. Merkuro Mail is part of "
"the Merkuro groupware suite and is currently in beta. For now, it only "
"allows you to read your emails."
msgstr ""
"«Merkuro Mail» sorburu irekiko e-posta bezero aske bat da. «Merkuro Mail» "
"«Merkuro» talde-lanerako aplikazio multzoaren atal bat da eta une honetan "
"beta egoeran dago. Oraingoz, e-postak irakurtzen besterik ez dizu uzten."

